4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become an AI Machine Learning Engineer," designed for individuals with no prior knowledge. Over a duration of 16 weeks, students will learn essential skills in Python, SQL, and Statistics, as well as how to create predictive models using libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. The course includes three classes per week, limited to 12 students per class, and certificates from recognized organizations are awarded upon completion. Classes can be conducted in either English or Spanish, making the program accessible to a broader audience. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop